{"id":22961,"title":"Use of naftifine hydrochloride 2% cream and 39% urea cream in the treatment of tinea pedis complicated by hyperkeratosis.","abstract":"The treatment of tinea pedis with hyperkeratosis has always been challenging due to presence of thick scales even after the resolution of active fungal infection. Patients usually identify hyperkeratosis with active disease. Therefore, a regimen of an antifungal and a keratolytic agent would be useful not only clearing the skin clinically but also addressing patients' perceptions.","date":"2014-02-10","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24509966","annotations":[{"name":"Urea","weight":0.854513,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Urea"},{"name":"Athlete's foot","weight":0.846603,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Athlete's_foot"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.804197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Antifungal medication","weight":0.790973,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antifungal_medication"},{"name":"Skin","weight":0.756683,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skin"},{"name":"Keratolytic","weight":0.742736,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keratolytic"},{"name":"Fungus","weight":0.734616,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fungus"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Mycosis","weight":0.701811,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mycosis"},{"name":"Tinea","weight":0.686781,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tinea"},{"name":"Naftifine","weight":0.677403,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naftifine"},{"name":"Hydrochloride","weight":0.631563,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hydrochloride"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.522042,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Cream","weight":0.12245,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cream"},{"name":"Hyperkeratosis","weight":0.119639,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperkeratosis"},{"name":"Perception","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perception"},{"name":"Scale (anatomy)","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scale_(anatomy)"},{"name":"Deforestation","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deforestation"},{"name":"Regimen","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Regimen"}]}
